title: Panoramic Views Home On Large Lot 17000 Eastwood FABULOUS
text:
Panoramic Views Home On Large Lot 17000 Eastwood FABULOUS ad date: 10/10/2015 
sprawling Ranch style 3-bedroom, 2-bath custom home. Located in beautiful Marina Heights neighborhood over-looking the river, city & Oregon coastline, city lights at night & incredible mountain views. Big rock fireplace, spacious rooms, full service wet bar. 1500 sq ft Trex Deck for entertaining. Sunny large acre plus lot with paved private road. Text the messagePORTVIEWto the phone number90210for an instant video tour. No.14060619 $385,000 Jude Hodge, Broker
